Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally narcissistic, selfish, greedy, people who only care about themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and spent their life kicking dogs, now learn what love is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what concern for another human, what another being is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin to pour themselves into that, and instantly, you know, they go over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question, but I'm wondering whether the dollar special is still in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on what you want for a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug for a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisses are more expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisses will cost you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so there's our...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he's been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where these dollars go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to all the people who help you in the airports,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and push the wheelchairs and turn you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They get them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wonderful in Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They all come from a certain place in Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're loving, wonderful people, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see one guy's carrying your baggage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and other people showing you where to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and other one's pushing the wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have an integrated lovingness with each other, communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They all come from someplace, Kenya or someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a stunning sort of integrity of who they are to the world, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sort of beautiful to watch, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They just, and they pass each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and they send each other loving messages as they pass the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a fun thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a fun thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Harkins, I just want to thank you for being my teacher for the last year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming since, I guess, February of 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I read your book, Power Versus Force, which helped me finish my book, The CEO Challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would just like to share that book with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with spirit and business, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirituality and business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've asked you, and I've heard you talk from the platform about CEOs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and your compassion for CEOs and the difficult job they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess my question is, you mentioned, I think, sometime earlier this week, this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that CEOs were somewhere at the 197 or 198 level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One time we did CEOs of the top 500 in Fortune magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was, I think, before the collapse of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the collapse of all those in and around some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess my question is, I've been working with CEOs my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a consultant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And what...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get CEOs to a 200 level?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the awareness they need in your experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Touche.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened is that the field, the overall field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which was at 190...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, until the late 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I numbers right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Moved up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the late 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of the harmonic concordance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, it went from 190, where it had been for many centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,jumped to 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the world of 205 is different than the world of 190, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can get away with at 190 is going to surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, like, now it's like oil and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it worse, on October 14th of last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it jumped from 205 to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if the overall field of consciousness is 207,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then that which is non-integrous is going to come to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be finessed out, like a poker game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was the old boy way of doing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A little here, a little there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just close our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wink at this and wink at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, in a more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In a more integrous field, that which is non-integrous begins to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One reason women CEOs, their companies did better,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,according to Fortune magazine in 2003,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason the companies run by women did better than those run by men
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is because women are new to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They watch their P's and Q's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not part of the old boy network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not used to closing their eyes to this little irregularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for which the other guy gets you favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, the women are very scrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the women are scrupulously honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll last for a generation or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they'll learn to play the old girl network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they're a little out of date,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but can't you just change the date on and ship it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's going to notice, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it's been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it don't work that way no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The field has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the non-Integrity CEO is going to have a tough time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At 190, he thrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At 207, he's going to be called into court.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, corporate America's cleaning house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Corporate America.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see it's celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If she just had a little humility,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't even be in jail, would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If she said, I'm sorry, I made a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all that was required.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that was required.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I'm sorry, I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody would have said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the fellow who was involved
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in a cult group in Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had emailed you some information on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful for Lou and Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All the cult stories are horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are worse than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they calibrated the group at like 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, we were involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife and two daughters are still involved in the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with the group for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the grace of God, I'm out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm in a custody battle with my 13-year-old daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been in the group three years and been brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm working to get custody of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is then, you gave us some great ideas for,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,just living the concepts of goodness, of patience, of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else that I can do for my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as reprogramming her and helping her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with her, the mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With the mother right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother's in the cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want her because the mother's in the cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're going through a divorce
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm trying to get custody of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On what basis are you going to get custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That she's involved in this cult group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, everybody's got a cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's that going to get you in court, just because you call it a cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're having a child advocate work with us on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have some professional opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In a child custody case, that may carry weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In a major case, that doesn't carry weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't carry weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That doesn't negate the mother's rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a right to freedom, to believe what she wants to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the fact that she's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the fact that you differ with her and you want to make her wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not a legal basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the group has done some pretty unscrupulous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they've done things that I don't want to even hear about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But is there anything like, you know, if I would get custody of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is there, you know, things that you would recommend reprogramming or?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I would recommend you go to Al-Anon because you're going to try force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're going to win with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to increase your own spiritual power so that that which you are attracts the resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't know what her karma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the court to negate her karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, you see, doing the Course in Miracles or doing the 12-step program,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in the office, I would tell you, go to Al-Anon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the basic principles of Al-Anon and apply it in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it will resolve itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, within the world, the world will do what you can within reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But then don't forget that force results in counterforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Attraction, there's no resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what kind of anguish you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And other than, you know, other than like joining in, I would join Al-Anon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to get the principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've got a heck of a problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The problems that you're running into are almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to save the drowning person, et cetera, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, you've got to be a savior here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, you say you've got multiple things going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need the spiritual strength of a group, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And their shared experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been through impossible situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the best legal advice you can get as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean to be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need, you're going to win it with power, not with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you've got enough legal basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have legal, I have an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got an attorney, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's got an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, has she been tortured, raped, burned, starved?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then how do you show child abuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you don't believe what they believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in a court of law, you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The real law of it is you don't have a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a case that I can hear of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that you allege that they're weird people inculcating your weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there has been some pretty, you know, some.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To them, you have very weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now you've got where you're at legally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I say to the other attorney, you've got really weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the truth of God, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from Master Blah Blah on the other side or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Nan, Jai Al-Nan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because of the wisdom and the strength there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't want to do this all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too ravaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You need friends, compadres.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let you get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go down the drain of the cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really frivolous, but what cat foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the way she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskers, fancy feasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mention some cat foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mention some cat foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you see on the supermarket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's that Purina cat chow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a cat yet, but I'm in the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll whisper to you which one not to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My cat to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I recalibrated those brands again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tried her on that same cat food that she turned her nose up at before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And fancy feasts is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, no, she turned it down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we recalibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, it was like $1.90.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In your last tape set that you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Nightingale-Conant one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned that when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have a date set for our death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered how you also mentioned several times
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have permission to leave whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have permission to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in that space, you're not controlled by karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you're beyond that, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're outside of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is no time in which you're going to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because your reality isn't in time to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the leaving this has to do with bodiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about when you talk about, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,getting into the culture in the downtown inner cities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and that and getting killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,would we not get killed unless it was the right date?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you're coming from a different context.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming from a different context.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying if it's when I'm said to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,why can't I just close my eyes when I'm driving
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,on the highway and be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get paralyzed for life, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be mangled, but I wouldn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're misconceiving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then what, where am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I have to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of yourself to the best of your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the reasons you'll probably live longer is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the way how that karma expresses itself with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, people say, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hadn't taken the vitamins all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have lived this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's because of the spirit in you lighting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,up your karmic inheritance that you value your life enough
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that, don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to make linear that which is not linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perceived within time, which is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't happen within time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the reality of that which you are doesn't shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so much a calendar time as a sequence time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you read with some teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that every single move you make was already preset
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at the moment you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you said and done in this life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so far, was already, already preset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the miracle says, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already lived this all, because you're calling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're calling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer is really that it's a linear idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's really .
