Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're destined to leave early,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be very careless about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you would probably do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my name is Kwasi Curry, and I'm from Littleton, Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is sort of built around the idea of holding on to things,
