Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to ask you if you would like to sell you a Cadillac car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To buy my Cadillac car?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, you have a fine Cadillac car, and he wants to know if you want to sell that Cadillac car.
