Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it weighed a lot, weighed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you backed into it, you got the dead-end fender, I didn't, so it was a big heavy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,.
