Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I pass on, I'll leave a note in my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.42,0:22:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your name and phone number, and we'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have it when I pass on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't need it after that.
