Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything I have to know for enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only want to thank you, Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask you to forgive me.
