Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for children,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching them the power of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that it can heal and so.
