Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.11,0:25:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd just like to ask for permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.11,0:25:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that your universe is one, fully complete,
