Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.75,0:26:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She says these books are by Pankhur-Hoopenton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.75,0:26:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's right.
