Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.06,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have what it takes to understand all the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of human consciousness within ourselves, and we will transcend that, and all questions
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,will be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of where it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.06,0:26:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be any questions to be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.06,0:26:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything becomes obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.06,0:27:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything becomes obvious, and there are only questions left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.83,0:27:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only questions we ask have to do with form and linearity and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.94,0:27:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To adjust the Rong or the practice or the communication the...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.94,0:27:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking into now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.88,0:27:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is witness to contextualize it in ways that are comprehensible to the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of themselves, they're meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.67,0:27:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But because you have to go that way on the highway,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.67,0:27:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody should leave the map of this is the right turn, this is the wrong turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.99,0:27:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that you won't get there, because your intention will eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.99,0:27:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of going this way and that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.35,0:27:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can give you another inch, I'm a rolfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.49,0:28:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.49,0:28:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.49,0:28:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cheating, he just saw me limping and he knows he's got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.49,0:28:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An inch and a half and I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.11,0:28:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the only shrinking of a quarter of an inch a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.00,0:28:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet get longer and you get shorter, it's like you're a Gumby Bear and you're like...
