Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.00,0:28:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be 5'7, I'm 5'5 and a half or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.77,0:28:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're puddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm puddling, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.90,0:28:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You slowly melt like a Gumby Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.11,0:28:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You get shorter and shorter and your feet get longer, is that funny or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if rolfing can do much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.11,0:28:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to make my feet shorter and make me taller, push it all back up the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.79,0:29:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.31,0:29:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the following question.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.31,0:29:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall on one of your last chapters of the Book of the Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.31,0:29:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the shortest cut or straight path for self-realization was to ask yourself, how am I aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.31,0:29:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how do I know that I even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.31,0:29:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know that I exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.42,0:29:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know that I exist or how do I know that I'm aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.42,0:29:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You look to the substrate of subjectivity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That out of which experiencing your own existence is arising.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.42,0:29:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.60,0:29:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, because in some moments I feel comfortable starting to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.60,0:29:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've also started with A Course in Miracles by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.60,0:29:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like, I'm in lesson like 35 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.44,0:29:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an easier or straighter or...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:29:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get there in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.46,0:30:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get there in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.16,0:30:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Start at 35 and do every fifth lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.59,0:30:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you only need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.59,0:30:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that one completely, it'll save you doing 364 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one, you can get the totality of it or you can get it piecemeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.68,0:30:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But surrendering is not something that people are familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.22,0:30:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.27,0:30:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They confuse it with being defeated, giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.75,0:30:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is a profound...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.03,0:31:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.03,0:31:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you totally give up, it's coming from a much greater depth than you'd realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.03,0:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you know why it was so hard to surrender things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.10,0:31:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that ego is ferocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, its tenacity is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.10,0:31:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it hangs on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.94,0:31:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.45,0:31:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A combination of your will empowered by the divine will that can overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.06,0:31:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.70,0:31:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus the conviction that it can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.15,0:31:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.15,0:31:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the value of a teacher, is it conveys the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.50,0:31:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, doctor, that's where my friend Jim, he's been kind of hard on your book,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but he'd still like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.50,0:31:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.50,0:31:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrated tai chi and yoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there's any other disciplines or sports in your upcoming book.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.50,0:32:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.75,0:32:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunbathing. We forgot sunbathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.75,0:32:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunbathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.75,0:32:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.75,0:32:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might take that up, but not if it was going to be like 35 or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.75,0:32:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we remembered archery, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.75,0:32:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever read Zen and the Art of Archery?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.75,0:32:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm reading now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.75,0:32:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.75,0:32:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we didn't calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.75,0:32:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.75,0:32:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is why we never finished the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.75,0:32:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.75,0:32:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll think of three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.75,0:32:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll think of three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.75,0:32:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get an email about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.75,0:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget who wrote back in 1622.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.75,0:32:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, and she'll say, I can't go anymore today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.75,0:32:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what was it you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.75,0:32:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wondered where archery would come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.75,0:32:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.75,0:32:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.75,0:32:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.75,0:32:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do archery?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.75,0:32:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.75,0:32:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do archery now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.84,0:32:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.84,0:32:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.84,0:32:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.84,0:32:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Archery is done by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.84,0:32:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.84,0:32:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.84,0:32:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.84,0:32:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.10,0:32:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.10,0:32:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.10,0:32:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.10,0:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.10,0:32:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.10,0:32:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.10,0:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it as the highest form of archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest form of archery calibrates over 360, 380, 390.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest form of archery calibrates over 390, 395.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.40,0:33:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's purity of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.40,0:33:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.43,0:33:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the way you learn to do it is to not think it and just let the arrow fly itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.46,0:33:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 390.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.46,0:33:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.46,0:33:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.58,0:33:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go a different archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.58,0:33:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of archery...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.58,0:33:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.58,0:33:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm envisioning the Zen archery calibrates over 450, 480, 475.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.58,0:33:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Zen archery is about 475.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.76,0:33:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary archery is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.76,0:33:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,390?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.76,0:33:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,390.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.76,0:33:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.76,0:33:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very high intention 390.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it up because without a thumb you can't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.83,0:33:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to give up the bagpipes and archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.16,0:33:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And playing the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:33:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And playing the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.16,0:34:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.16,0:34:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will play a musical instrument the next lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.33,0:34:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will play a musical instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.33,0:34:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.46,0:34:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll make music.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.19,0:34:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like some clarification about where...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.19,0:34:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.19,0:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like some clarification about where the expression of love and compassion run into
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,or where they run out and where interfering with people's lives, interfering with their
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.71,0:34:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.71,0:34:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.71,0:34:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know where love and compassion for mankind comes in and where interfering
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.63,0:34:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with their destiny or lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.63,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the life?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a very sophisticated question.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, on a calibration scale, love calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.67,0:34:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a me-you kind of a relationship until you get to a higher state in which love is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.67,0:34:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.67,0:34:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how you apply it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.69,0:34:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How you perceive life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How you understand life is different at the various levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.69,0:35:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.69,0:35:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When does it become interfering with one's life, with another person's karma or...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.09,0:35:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.09,0:35:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.09,0:35:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.21,0:35:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a sensitivity of knowing when intervention is appropriate, when it's appropriate and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.82,0:35:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when it is inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you know kinesiology, I might ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.42,0:35:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I might say, this is the person's karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.42,0:35:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It would serve the highest good for me to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.55,0:35:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.61,0:35:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a way of finding, because it's a complex question, a simple answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.78,0:35:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the highest good, it would be best that I intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.09,0:36:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.09,0:36:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In a situation I'm thinking about now, we got no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.65,0:36:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That lesson can only be learned by hitting bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.30,0:36:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I suggest, a lot of times, Al-Anon, because the temptation there is to try to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,intervene and keep the person from hitting bottom, when it's by hitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That hitting bottom is the source of their salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're doing is killing them, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.30,0:36:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You pay all their bills, they can't pay them anymore, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.61,0:36:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.61,0:36:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you follow a spiritual group, the whole way of looking at it of Al-Anon, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way of looking at it, of course, in miracles, you could use kinesiology to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.61,0:36:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ask specifically, you know, what's my karmic...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.03,0:36:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's coming up for me karmically?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.03,0:36:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just what the other person...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.51,0:37:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a lesson where you learn to be self-sacrificing for the good of something
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.51,0:37:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.51,0:37:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it could be that you've got a program.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.86,0:37:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.15,0:37:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.15,0:37:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To see what kind of a program you're fooling yourself into thinking you're doing it for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.25,0:37:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.25,0:37:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The commonest program is to prove that you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.34,0:37:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone's lying by the roadside, needs help?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.01,0:37:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You do what's automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.01,0:37:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.53,0:37:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive on, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.98,0:37:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving to charities?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.98,0:37:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Good Samaritan lived in a different era.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.98,0:37:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But giving to charities?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.98,0:37:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.98,0:37:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving to charities?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.98,0:37:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving money?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:37:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about charities?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.30,0:38:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that interviewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.84,0:38:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that which is appropriate to the level that you're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.84,0:38:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there is no absolute answer to the question, because it would depend on where the person
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.28,0:38:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is at in their own evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.28,0:38:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a point at which the lesson is to stop by the self-sacrificing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a point at which the lesson is to stop by the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.28,0:38:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a very advanced lesson where the lesson is not to stop by the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.28,0:38:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it takes a great deal of discernment to know which is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.48,0:38:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.48,0:38:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And could I have a hug, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.48,0:38:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.48,0:38:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.86,0:38:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.86,0:38:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.51,0:38:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to New Zealand for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.96,0:38:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.96,0:38:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, when are you being an enabler, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.59,0:38:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a subtle question.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.59,0:38:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.59,0:39:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on what lesson is being learned at this time by both people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.13,0:39:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I think physiology in the name of the highest good, which would be the best
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.13,0:39:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,way to go when you really can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.13,0:39:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I first want to say I'm grateful for your consciousness, because I definitely am feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.69,0:39:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is almost like I can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.69,0:39:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question was about when spiritual energy begins to move, do you have any words of wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,state of being, blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.86,0:39:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak directly into the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.86,0:39:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.90,0:39:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.90,0:39:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.90,0:39:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.90,0:39:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just saying when people begin to feel spiritual energy, their brain, whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.65,0:39:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,start moving to them, do you have any words of wisdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.65,0:39:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any states of being or blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.65,0:39:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The movement to kind of lend the energy into the brain is exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.65,0:39:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It may last for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.65,0:39:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted, I don't know, five, seven years, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.65,0:39:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.65,0:39:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.65,0:39:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.65,0:39:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.65,0:39:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.17,0:39:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.17,0:39:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.17,0:39:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.17,0:39:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.51,0:39:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.25,0:39:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.25,0:40:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.76,0:40:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.76,0:40:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.19,0:40:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you focus your attention at one side of the brain you'll feel it blow, flow more
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.23,0:40:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.36,0:40:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you focus your attention over here you'll feel it more into this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.88,0:40:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do about it except be thankful and enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.61,0:40:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fizlan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.90,0:40:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've reached a real block.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I have, I've reached a real pinnacle of intellectual understanding spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.51,0:40:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have a lot of spiritual realizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.25,0:40:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's like stuck there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.59,0:40:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like all these questions I'm asking is just running in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.48,0:40:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All this reading is just running in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.67,0:41:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know to take that jump into the subjective, it's like the last step is taken by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.84,0:41:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do I kick that door in?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.78,0:41:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what am I doing or not doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.36,0:41:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a thorn in my mind that I just cannot get rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.13,0:41:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get rid of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.23,0:41:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.65,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm just stuck in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm at this wall that I cannot break through to get to the subjective actual experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.59,0:41:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.32,0:41:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't experience the actual...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.86,0:41:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're trying to achieve something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.03,0:41:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.59,0:41:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.67,0:41:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let yourself be defeated by the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.78,0:41:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.48,0:41:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.13,0:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.07,0:41:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was pretty easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.92,0:41:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.05,0:41:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's trying to solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.17,0:41:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen koan, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.55,0:41:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally you surrender and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.92,0:41:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But then also, a part of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:41:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have a lot of obligations to people in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.32,0:42:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I say a lot of things like, you know, I'm going to be here to help you through this business thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.51,0:42:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.30,0:42:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like a tie to these obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.96,0:42:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel like if I take that step, I'm going to be so out of it that I'm not even going to be functioning in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.38,0:42:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know you're going to be out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.21,0:42:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.98,0:42:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have this, you know, it's like a fear or a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you look so new.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.19,0:42:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't have something to help me drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.01,0:42:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if I become enlightened, the business is going to go down in the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.17,0:42:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.71,0:42:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.07,0:42:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.96,0:42:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.21,0:42:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.15,0:42:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, that is a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.51,0:42:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.40,0:42:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Put off being enlightened until you finish the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.00,0:42:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're unable to function and support yourself, it'll be God's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.36,0:42:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he doesn't, then you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.28,0:42:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.21,0:42:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.57,0:43:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.25,0:43:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.26,0:43:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.51,0:43:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can probably buy his company cheap right now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.75,0:43:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you for sharing your sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.59,0:43:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I very much enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.44,0:43:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm here with a group of ten people from around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.05,0:43:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working to manifest a theater in the Sedona area,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.38,0:43:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has to do with helping people find their heart
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.28,0:43:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and using...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.11,0:43:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...marionettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.11,0:43:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought some information.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.11,0:43:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd simply like to leave it...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.11,0:43:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.11,0:43:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...if that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.42,0:43:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.42,0:43:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that could find his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.42,0:43:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The ten woodmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.42,0:43:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.42,0:43:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.42,0:43:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.42,0:43:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The ten woodmen didn't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.42,0:43:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they had to get him a heart, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.42,0:43:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.42,0:43:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.42,0:43:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.42,0:43:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.61,0:44:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can provide any insight in understanding the...or insight on communication with the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.84,0:44:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,higher self and what that experience feels like in contrast to the...and discernment
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.84,0:44:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the admonitions you gave about the astral and such to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.03,0:44:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, how would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you can say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.03,0:44:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've asked me three or four questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the first question?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.03,0:44:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can provide insight on how to know when you're communicating with the higher
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.03,0:44:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,self, when you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.03,0:44:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't try and communicate with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.03,0:44:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.57,0:44:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your higher self's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.57,0:44:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you're setting up a dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.57,0:44:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a me and then there's my higher self.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.57,0:44:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.57,0:44:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're projecting a separation which doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.57,0:44:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.92,0:44:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You just be what you're inspired to be, thereby fulfilling your destiny and the working
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.92,0:44:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,out of whatever karmic momentums you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.92,0:44:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's to do what you're doing, then that is to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.94,0:44:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.94,0:44:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.94,0:44:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.21,0:44:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.21,0:44:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.21,0:44:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.21,0:44:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.21,0:44:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.21,0:44:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.50,0:44:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.50,0:45:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.50,0:45:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.50,0:45:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.50,0:45:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.50,0:45:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.50,0:45:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.53,0:45:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.53,0:45:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.53,0:45:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.53,0:45:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the artistic expression that it's taking at this particular point.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.42,0:45:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't like there's a you and then your higher self.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.13,0:45:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your higher self is what...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.75,0:45:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Guides you, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.51,0:45:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.67,0:45:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, I'm alive because of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.15,0:45:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for the ego, I'd forget to take my vitamin pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.23,0:45:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's because of the spirit that your ego values taking vitamin pills and supporting
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.48,0:45:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.23,0:45:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still coming out of the spiritual field.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.30,0:45:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.38,0:45:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you feel inspired to do this at this time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.03,0:45:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the right way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.63,0:45:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.21,0:45:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still trying to understand the concept of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.73,0:46:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the fact that nothing causes anything else to happen mean
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.76,0:46:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that when I go to play golf next Tuesday and hit that ball wherever it goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.42,0:46:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't cause that to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.00,0:46:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause would be a grandiose delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.78,0:46:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that creation unfolding?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.05,0:46:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.61,0:46:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.38,0:46:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the propensity, you release the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.76,0:46:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me use a different analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.63,0:46:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot force an apple to fall to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.57,0:46:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you snip the stem, the apple falls to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.11,0:46:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't cause it to fall to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.53,0:46:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you triggered the release of the golf ball, but then you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.63,0:46:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.11,0:46:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I drop that, I didn't cause it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.65,0:47:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravity did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.61,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.48,0:47:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say I caused it to fall, then you are greater than the power of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.88,0:47:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you must be divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.32,0:47:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.36,0:47:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As the ego is claiming authorship, claiming the qualities of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.65,0:47:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why it sees things out there that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.48,0:47:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because that way it can still maintain that it really is omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.78,0:47:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, as you can see from the apple falling from the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.82,0:47:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.46,0:47:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you release the potentiality by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.42,0:47:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.01,0:47:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, what's his name's latest book?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.00,0:47:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.73,0:47:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.15,0:47:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So intentionality then, you might say, sets the program,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.86,0:47:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but the unfolding of the program is up to karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.94,0:48:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the power of intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.44,0:48:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the power of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.86,0:48:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.46,0:48:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, it's the same as an apple dropping from the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.09,0:48:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention releases a potentiality to become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.09,0:48:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't create any of those, but you are the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.59,0:48:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.55,0:48:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico suggested that perhaps I should ask that of Susan,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.75,0:48:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but you two can decide, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.57,0:48:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some tips about calibrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.61,0:48:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to calibrate all the usual things, cat food, people, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.51,0:48:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, I'm getting no kind of, they're very arbitrary calibrations, seemingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.86,0:48:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get two answers the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.01,0:48:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes practice, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.34,0:48:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a good partner to work with?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.25,0:48:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Which microphone is the one you're talking into?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.32,0:48:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to talk into the silver one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.40,0:49:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your microphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.40,0:49:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one I'm talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.36,0:49:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.63,0:49:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes to the video camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.61,0:49:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.76,0:49:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.17,0:49:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the silver one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.19,0:49:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.86,0:49:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.76,0:49:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.44,0:49:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what is the question again?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.65,0:49:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking about some tips about calibrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.38,0:49:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting no consistency in my calibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.34,0:49:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.92,0:49:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to calibrate the usual things.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.17,0:49:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing it by yourself or with a partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.88,0:49:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.63,0:49:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.67,0:49:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.65,0:49:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We go over the basics of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.57,0:49:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We got time to go over the basics one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.46,0:49:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.69,0:49:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.61,0:49:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do the basics of kinesiology again?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.61,0:49:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.71,0:49:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Both people have to calibrate integrously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.26,0:49:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention of the question has to be integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.46,0:49:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, seeking gain may bias, so you don't want to bias the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.21,0:49:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what archery calibrates at, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.19,0:50:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at, now, in my mind, I can hold different visions of archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.26,0:50:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains why sometimes you get different calibrations for the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.51,0:50:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You always have to hold the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.75,0:50:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're a visual person, all right, now I'm looking at medieval archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.71,0:50:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at a courtyard, and I'm looking at it as a military discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.90,0:50:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the royal archers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.38,0:50:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The royal archers calibrate over 480, 430, calibrate over 390, 395.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.90,0:50:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfection of archery then as a discipline is 390.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.78,0:50:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, with Zen, you're looking at a different kind of archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.46,0:50:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm looking at, um, I'm looking at the bow releasing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.28,0:50:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm doing Zen archery, I don't aim at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:51:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm doing military archery, I aim, I have an estimation of the wind, the number of yards,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.13,0:51:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how many pounds pulled there is on this bow, I know the design, I've feathered the arrows myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.19,0:51:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can pretty well guarantee that I'll fall within a certain designation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.78,0:51:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very complicated area.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.73,0:51:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice makes that perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.73,0:51:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's another way of doing archery, which is the way I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.42,0:51:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by all the people walking around with band-aids.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one to release, release it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.73,0:51:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one releasing it, and there's nothing happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.73,0:51:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole phenomena is a unitary oneness unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.73,0:51:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh, to the witnessing of perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.61,0:51:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's various ways of doing it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.61,0:51:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the way we do it then is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.65,0:52:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I press down with how many ounces would you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.65,0:52:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than two ounces, three ounces, four ounces, five ounces, more than six ounces, more than five ounces, about five ounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.13,0:52:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just one finger pressing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.13,0:52:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so she resists, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.13,0:52:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,equal to the pressure pressing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.55,0:52:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the answer is quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.05,0:52:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen archery calibrates over 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.51,0:52:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I don't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.51,0:52:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say, Zen archery calibrates over 400, then I wait a minute while I talk to you, and then I push her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.51,0:52:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So the kinesiologic response through the acupuncture system is very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.21,0:52:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So she'll tell you, in fact, I also, the minute I answer, ask the question, I already feel the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.21,0:52:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and she feels it running down her arm, and now it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.50,0:52:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.98,0:53:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.84,0:53:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're detached, it's irrelevant what the answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.84,0:53:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.84,0:53:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there's a way you can corroborate the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.59,0:53:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If a certain thing, the answer to that is yes, then many other things would follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.59,0:53:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can cross-check the validity of an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.59,0:53:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, now, you don't want any background music.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.46,0:53:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best, uh, to not have metal crossing in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.84,0:53:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's steel belts, glasses, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you don't want to do it in a loving way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.67,0:53:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it in a detached, clinical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.69,0:53:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we're smiling at each other and thinking of lovely things,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.90,0:53:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna get a false positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.90,0:53:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.90,0:53:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm radiating love towards her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.90,0:53:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you act detached, clinical, doctor-patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.90,0:53:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself as a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.21,0:53:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only interested in the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.21,0:54:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got no investment in the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.30,0:54:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The figures you get, it doesn't make any difference what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.30,0:54:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come out different than what you expect, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.30,0:54:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, with further inquiry, you can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.30,0:54:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, if you're getting false answers, the other thing, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.30,0:54:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be contaminated by heavy metal music and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.30,0:54:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you listen to music, uh, MTV and that kind of music,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.30,0:54:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, killer rapster rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.30,0:54:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.67,0:54:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick your pregnant wife in the belly, and if that don't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.38,0:54:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,blow her away with a hollow bullet kind of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.38,0:54:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find that you, uh, the acupuncture is blown,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.38,0:54:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the system is blown for about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.63,0:54:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you've been in the radio, in the car, and your radio is playing,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.69,0:54:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some of that's played as background music to advertisements.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.69,0:54:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got programmed without knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.57,0:54:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could clear it doing the thymic thump, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.57,0:55:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. uh, Diamond, John Diamond, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.17,0:55:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we showed the, the effect on the thymus of negativity is suppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.17,0:55:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pound, the thymus is right behind the breastbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.17,0:55:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You pound on the thymus, I won't do it because I got a microphone on,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.17,0:55:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but you go, ha ha ha, ha ha ha, ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.17,0:55:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, and while you're doing it, you just smile and think of someone you love,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.17,0:55:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or your kitty, or your grandmother, or whatever, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.17,0:55:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now that rebalances your acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.17,0:55:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, sometimes certain people don't work well together for karmic reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.07,0:55:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes husbands don't work well together for karmic reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.07,0:55:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes husbands and wives can't use each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.07,0:55:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sometimes have to experiment and maybe go to a class on it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.13,0:55:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and find somebody that you can work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.13,0:55:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it takes practice like riding a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.13,0:55:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, it's a subtlety, it's a subtlety.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.13,0:55:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And people look for something gross, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.13,0:55:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we were in Korea, we had a heck of a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.13,0:55:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we couldn't get anybody to go, you know, say no to anything
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.13,0:55:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were like into anti-gravity, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.13,0:56:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The harder you push, the harder they push back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.13,0:56:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a mesomorphic struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.13,0:56:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a, it's not strength, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.13,0:56:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.23,0:56:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's ways of doing it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.23,0:56:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's fingers like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.23,0:56:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold them tightly together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.23,0:56:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You picture Ben Loudon and pull as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.23,0:56:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you alternate.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.23,0:56:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You picture Abraham Lincoln and you pull as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.23,0:56:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see there's a difference in strength, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.65,0:56:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And if all those things don't work, give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.42,0:56:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.53,0:56:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.53,0:56:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, there's certain things that can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.38,0:56:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, let's do the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.73,0:56:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have permission to do the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.73,0:56:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience energy before and after lecture went up over nine points,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.73,0:57:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points, 12 points, 14 points, 15 points, 12 points, 15 points, 12 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.21,0:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big jump in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.21,0:57:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The average human being evolves five points in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.63,0:57:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience collectively went up 10 points this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.36,0:57:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means some people went up over 100
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.36,0:57:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and some people weren't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.61,0:57:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in a while, the question and answer thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.61,0:57:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,people will ask me a question and I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.61,0:57:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,were you with the lecture today?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.61,0:57:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll ask me something that the whole lecture was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.61,0:57:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to advance myself spiritually?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.61,0:57:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, eight hours of talking, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.23,0:57:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they ask me, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.61,0:57:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.90,0:57:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hoggins, thank you for your service to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.90,0:57:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.61,0:57:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I serve a church as its pastor,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.61,0:58:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm wanting to find a way to describe or explain the role of conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.21,0:58:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is a common impression that it is something that happens outside oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.21,0:58:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,such as the Holy Spirit, which appeared in one part of Scripture to be external.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.46,0:58:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be external, but anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.46,0:58:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the world of the duality and linear domain and Newtonian domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.71,0:58:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it would seem like it's external.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.71,0:58:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, it's an internal propensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.71,0:58:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you open the gate to it with your own consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.71,0:58:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By your own consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.86,0:58:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.23,0:58:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.61,0:58:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I commit myself to thee, O Lord, and to thy truth and to thy divine love,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.01,0:58:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hold back nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.21,0:58:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.21,0:58:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They should quit going to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.21,0:58:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.21,0:58:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.21,0:59:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.21,0:59:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that, don't worry, threaten him with hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.21,0:59:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There, hell, baby, you pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.63,0:59:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.50,0:59:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.90,0:59:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Tammy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.90,0:59:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Oklahoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.90,0:59:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I come, I'm sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.67,0:59:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of what question to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.67,0:59:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been consulting a higher self, even though there isn't really a higher self,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.13,0:59:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.13,0:59:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been standing in line as to what the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.13,0:59:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.75,0:59:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the question that I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.75,0:59:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were going to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.75,1:00:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I might say, she's going to ask him,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.03,1:00:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.03,1:00:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.61,1:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.36,1:00:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.23,1:00:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.46,1:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting into why it's into the separation, the duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.44,1:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's an intellectualization.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.53,1:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to know the answer to that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.53,1:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.59,1:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.59,1:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.46,1:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so ultra simple, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.46,1:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.84,1:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.84,1:00:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See, to think about it, that's easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.84,1:00:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doing that for lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.73,1:01:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To just be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.73,1:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.50,1:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the power to be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.69,1:01:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.69,1:01:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the power to be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.69,1:01:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.69,1:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be just what you just sensed this second.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.69,1:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be that, because that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.94,1:01:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.94,1:01:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.94,1:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.94,1:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,May I share it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.94,1:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's celebrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.94,1:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.94,1:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw what I was seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.94,1:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw what I was seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.94,1:01:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.94,1:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.98,1:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.98,1:01:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.71,1:01:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.03,1:01:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.76,1:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you for allowing me to find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.76,1:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.76,1:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see in you a great teacher of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.76,1:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You have raised the calibrations of this world many, many times over.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.86,1:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And vibrations are raised because of your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.86,1:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspired by you when I first met you, I asked you about the presidency of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.86,1:02:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said it calibrates between 400 and 500?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.98,1:02:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The presidency calibrates 460.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.98,1:02:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.98,1:02:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.98,1:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspired by that, I wrote a prayer for the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.98,1:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.98,1:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, I'll read it or I'll give it to you, whatever you think proper.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.98,1:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is a one-page prayer for the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.98,1:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.98,1:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a generic prayer for whoever becomes president.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.98,1:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They all need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.98,1:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.98,1:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.98,1:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.98,1:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.98,1:02:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.98,1:02:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.98,1:02:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.98,1:02:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.98,1:02:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.98,1:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.98,1:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.98,1:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.98,1:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.09,1:02:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.09,1:02:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.09,1:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.09,1:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.09,1:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we have got time to read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.09,1:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.09,1:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.09,1:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one page.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.09,1:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will value it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.09,1:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.78,1:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.78,1:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Manthush.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.78,1:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the forthcoming book, there's a chapter on America.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.88,1:03:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the truth about America?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.23,1:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody seems to get what is the truth about America.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.23,1:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there was, of course, a great book written about it by a Frenchman.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.55,1:03:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about democracy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.55,1:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's its name?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.55,1:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.55,1:03:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.09,1:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, people seem to have difficulty in finding out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.38,1:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I read an article, an article editorial in Arizona Republic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.67,1:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.25,1:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten points.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.25,1:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What America is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.30,1:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, God, where did she come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.30,1:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.30,1:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it with absolute clarity, purity of heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.30,1:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw the heart of America.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.30,1:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw the heart of America.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.30,1:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.30,1:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was way up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.30,1:03:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I wrote her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.30,1:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, you know, I would, in this chapter on America, it's so maligned.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.30,1:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't even know what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.30,1:04:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I would like the privilege to reprint it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.34,1:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Manthush came up and gave me permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.34,1:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the book on America, you'll see her name and the ten points of what America is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.34,1:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she comes from a different culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.34,1:04:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She comes in and sees it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.34,1:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.34,1:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And she wrote it with great simplicity and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.34,1:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm very thankful to have you here today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.34,1:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're honored by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.34,1:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have your permission, according to the Indian tradition, when we meet a great teacher, we touch his feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.34,1:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the tradition.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.34,1:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.34,1:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.40,1:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Manthush.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.40,1:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.40,1:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from India.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.11,1:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Americans may not know what America is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.05,1:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a great place.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.05,1:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's pretty clear to her what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.05,1:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'll get to read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.05,1:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got time to read it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.32,1:05:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a masterful job.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.96,1:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.53,1:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.53,1:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.53,1:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm new to your works.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.53,1:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in Toronto and I live in Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.53,1:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Wayne Dyer spoke of your book very highly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.53,1:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bought your book that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.53,1:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you appeared in Toronto, I was in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.53,1:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.53,1:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I did get back down yesterday to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.53,1:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd have seen you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.53,1:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Dr. Zee Gang Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.75,1:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the, I've been searching for a path.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.75,1:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering how do people like myself avoid getting into, I don't know, for lack of a better word, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.75,1:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost cult-like things.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.75,1:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.75,1:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's one of the reasons I wrote the book that's about to be published.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.75,1:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's about 30 ways to differentiate the true from the false.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.75,1:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,30 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.88,1:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just give you a brief of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.26,1:06:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to be done here in what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.26,1:06:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got enough time to finish everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.26,1:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're five.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.26,1:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.26,1:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Five's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.26,1:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.26,1:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.00,1:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.53,1:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.53,1:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.53,1:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same throughout all ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.53,1:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Every enlightenment is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.30,1:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.30,1:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Every mystic has said exactly the same thing in all cultures and in all times and in all generations.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.55,1:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That which sounds weird probably is.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.92,1:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a true spiritual teaching seeks nothing for itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.50,1:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.50,1:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want anything from the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.50,1:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.50,1:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want to control anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.17,1:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't try to enroll people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.01,1:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a pyramid structure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.01,1:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not multi-layered marketing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.01,1:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get brownie points for bringing in a convert.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.78,1:07:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no converts.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.78,1:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People are free to come and go without question.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.78,1:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is only a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.61,1:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoids adulation titled self-aggrandizement.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.61,1:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoids seduction by spiritual trappings.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.71,1:07:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Has no need for edifices.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.03,1:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not out to impress anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.03,1:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither gains nor loses.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.32,1:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether people attend or listen or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.15,1:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no real opinion on outside issues.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.86,1:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It will tell you the truth of what it thinks it sees.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.86,1:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.86,1:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.53,1:08:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No subscription.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.53,1:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No membership.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.53,1:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No dues.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.53,1:08:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No obligations.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.57,1:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A true spiritual teacher is not interested in how you dress.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.17,1:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.17,1:08:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family or your sex life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.17,1:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what you eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.93,1:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't prescribe any weird diets, exercises, contortions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.77,1:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does not advise altered states of consciousness brought about by altered breathing patterns, exercise patterns, biofeedback and things like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.52,1:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it has no doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.93,1:08:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It is essentially non-dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.93,1:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing a teacher could say that would be true would have been true of all the great teachers throughout all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.01,1:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which illuminates, that which comes forth is the reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.01,1:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.48,1:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is never different.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.27,1:09:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it recognizes no partiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.27,1:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No specialness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.27,1:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person is within a group like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.60,1:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What they are because of their particular energies, talents, muscles or lack thereof.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.92,1:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.92,1:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's pristine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.39,1:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.61,1:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.61,1:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want to own anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.42,1:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seek any kind of converts, gain, power over others.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.60,1:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.60,1:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that attracts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.60,1:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So it attracts those who are interested in that kind of an evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.97,1:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the leader or the teacher is not treated with any kind of specialness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.36,1:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Any kind of ooh-ah every time his name is mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.56,1:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.56,1:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And his picture goes up on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.56,1:10:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody goes ooh-ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.56,1:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's seduction by glamorization.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.57,1:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With the music and the hair and the sandals and the bald head.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.85,1:10:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.85,1:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.85,1:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The pseudo-poverty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.02,1:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.25,1:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So self-dramatization would tell you that they're out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.25,1:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the theatrics, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.25,1:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the 32-piece band?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.25,1:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, what is the program?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.97,1:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.97,1:11:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I met this gentleman through the Learning Annex.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.05,1:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was appearing with Sri Baba who I felt was a...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.05,1:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I put the two together.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.05,1:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's sometimes difficult to differentiate.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.05,1:11:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're on the same stage together.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.65,1:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's lineages that have been going on for thousands of years, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.81,1:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So some entity on the other side, you know, that it was discovered in 1973, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.85,1:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is unlikely to be divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.85,1:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.18,1:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Gingong on the other side, it tells you to sell everything and buy horses or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.18,1:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.18,1:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.18,1:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming back to Toronto?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.18,1:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Toronto. It's a beautiful city.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.26,1:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that's where we met Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.26,1:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that's where we heard of Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.26,1:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it when I got home.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.26,1:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Elvis was on the front page of the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.26,1:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy had, what was it, 18 high-powered rifles, 6,000 rounds of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.77,1:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And Elvis with a frisbee in his mouth runs up to this guy and goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.77,1:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the guy says, Jesus, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.77,1:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn himself in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.77,1:12:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.77,1:12:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.77,1:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To arrange while I was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.77,1:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.77,1:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I love Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.77,1:12:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a beautiful, beautiful city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.77,1:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.77,1:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can have a hug, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.77,1:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.77,1:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.77,1:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, love Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.77,1:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.80,1:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much like Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.80,1:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated very high, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.80,1:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are lost and can't find themselves, Chicago calibrates at 445.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.11,1:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.11,1:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.93,1:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.93,1:12:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.93,1:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.97,1:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.97,1:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.97,1:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.89,1:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.10,1:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.10,1:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a big city.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.10,1:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.10,1:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get my CD?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.10,1:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.10,1:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I sent it to the office.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.10,1:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.10,1:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, action!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.10,1:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.10,1:13:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.10,1:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank your wife for encouraging you to not even come out alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.27,1:13:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to do it throughout.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.52,1:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You better shout at your olvies.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.36,1:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.48,1:13:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.26,1:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with experiencing everything as not being separate
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.92,1:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and feeling the love and feeling that nothing is solid
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.18,1:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and that everything is transparent
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.93,1:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to encourage that to come and stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.34,1:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to own it. Don't try and control it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.26,1:14:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual experience, as you move up, will, as I said during the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.50,1:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you sometimes move ahead of your karma
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.06,1:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're floating above your karma and you're in an excellent space
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.93,1:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and then your karma catches up with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.26,1:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can be like in a beatific space and then it will fade away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.60,1:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the beatific space is to give you an advance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.11,1:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of how it's going to be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.50,1:14:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of mourning that it has left,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.31,1:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,take that as encouragement that you're on the right track
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.07,1:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because people who are not headed in a spiritual direction
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.50,1:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are not having psychedelic beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.72,1:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful experiences of the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.97,1:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Except with the odd chemical assistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.63,1:14:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it means it's encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.00,1:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You just continue in that direction, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.03,1:14:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hardest thing I think to learn about it all is patience.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.22,1:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That the phenomena has to unfold of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.28,1:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena have to, the phenomena unfold as the field can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.77,1:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to force it,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.31,1:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if you try to force it past what the field can hold you can fragment.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.48,1:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I used to be a consultant with the Zen Monastery
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.94,1:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the simultaneously Episcopal Catholic Diocese
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.85,1:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the places what they call them communities of nuns, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.23,1:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would sometimes see people trying to force a level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.57,1:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,faster than what their consciousness can handle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.18,1:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would have like, you know, nervous breakdowns, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.27,1:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it, let it, the rapidity with which it then evolves be up to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.46,1:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Also there's changes that you can see in brain function.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.02,1:15:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's changes in the nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.52,1:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Past certain points there's very agonizing things even that can happen in the nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.06,1:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a certain speed, I think, as you evolve, I think the nerves, the protein in the nerves,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.52,1:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the nerves literally begin to increase their capacity to carry energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.61,1:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact resist, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.61,1:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you speed up, see, because you're talking about logarithmic power,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.97,1:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you think moving from 410 to 420 is not that all big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.97,1:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a logarithm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.02,1:16:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,410 to 420 is a big energy jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.02,1:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I notice audiences very often collectively go about the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.02,1:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess would be physiologically that is the optimal.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.89,1:16:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You move faster than that and you'll start having, you might say,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.06,1:16:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,side effects from trying to force the kundalini too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.06,1:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And a major jump in consciousness can have major physiologic downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.17,1:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look up the encyclopedia, Britannica, mystics, you'll see the mystics of history.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.84,1:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the advices is be prepared to spend six months of the year in bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.84,1:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's moving it too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.89,1:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, sometimes you can't hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.10,1:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And so be content with however it goes and just constantly ask for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.94,1:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And be as gentle and loving towards yourself and everyone as you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.94,1:17:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the field moves of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.94,1:17:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It fuels its own capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.94,1:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to do high jumps before you've mastered the things because it's almost like a gym.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.23,1:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, don't try certain things until you build up the muscles
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.23,1:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.73,1:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What if everything you believe in is true and suddenly it collapses?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.73,1:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you handle that?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.73,1:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It will shock the nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.93,1:18:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.78,1:18:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, your body, your physiology is already building up to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.97,1:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.97,1:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're moving perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.65,1:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let divinity decide, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.65,1:18:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.97,1:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.97,1:18:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.97,1:18:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.30,1:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the bagpipes calibrate over 500, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.75,1:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagpipes, 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.53,1:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.14,1:18:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.25,1:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.25,1:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of 20 questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.25,1:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.25,1:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The self answers them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.25,1:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.25,1:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That happens, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.25,1:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.63,1:18:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.77,1:18:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.77,1:18:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Questions just occur in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.77,1:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You just answered it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.77,1:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.77,1:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.77,1:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.77,1:19:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what was it I was going to ask?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.77,1:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.77,1:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A fairly new visitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.02,1:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Community activist, sometimes office holder, and hopefully states person.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.02,1:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But a concern I've got is when you look at those people you're trying to help, and yet
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.02,1:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when you all could let the energy for an awful lot of people is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.27,1:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.27,1:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.27,1:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.27,1:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.27,1:19:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.27,1:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.27,1:19:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.27,1:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.34,1:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.34,1:19:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.34,1:19:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.34,1:19:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.34,1:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.34,1:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.34,1:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.43,1:19:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.43,1:19:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.43,1:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.43,1:19:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.43,1:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the energy for an awful lot of people is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.44,1:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you or should we be out there trying and how do we try to move people again if
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.81,1:19:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we want them to have their own freedom, but how do we help or should we try to help people
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.98,1:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,move into a better society and an environment?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.94,1:19:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well they teachers serves a function.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.84,1:20:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think through inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.57,1:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Through inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.31,1:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, that's one of the functions of the hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.43,1:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In Freudian terminology, there's the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.10,1:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also what's called the ego ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.28,1:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego ideal is those who become heroes to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.78,1:20:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We pattern ourself after them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.89,1:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the yardstick by which we measure ourself henceforth in life,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.22,1:20:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,consciously or unconsciously,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.57,1:20:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be that which is heroic to those who need a hero,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.88,1:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to demonstrate what that looks like, how that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.31,1:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to lift the overall field of consciousness by intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.36,1:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As they say, as you raise the level of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.77,1:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all the ships on the ocean are effortlessly raised at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.80,1:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in what Bill Cosby said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.97,1:20:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was dead right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.22,1:21:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's needed is less excusing, less blaming,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.52,1:21:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot more inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.64,1:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard work.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.88,1:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What he was saying is that the way out, the way up,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.34,1:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is by emphasizing the importance of the things that we call spiritual basics,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.52,1:21:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,responsibility, answerability,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.27,1:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to find the joy in being all that you can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.93,1:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees them as brainwashed into failure
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.81,1:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and using the perpetrator victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.39,1:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees them as being victimized by that kind of ideology,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.40,1:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's pissed about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.36,1:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a father, he's saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.78,1:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,don't fall for all this crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.13,1:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get working, get moving, get a bicycle, get a paper route,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.00,1:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,make some bucks, respect yourself and everybody around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.21,1:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, pick up the litter,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.71,1:22:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can't come out of it when surrounded by litter.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.48,1:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So to energize self-esteem, the value of self-esteem,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.72,1:22:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,true self-esteem,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.18,1:22:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,not self-esteem that's stolen by kicking down others,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.97,1:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,see, that's not real self-esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.15,1:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cheating your way to it, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.05,1:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I like what Cosby said.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.18,1:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.35,1:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty high, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.67,1:22:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying it was the father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.93,1:22:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.47,1:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, many of the children that he's talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.27,1:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.68,1:22:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So the men, I think,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.44,1:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody thinks it's the mother's got a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.47,1:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.43,1:22:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the father's got a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.82,1:22:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no father.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.46,1:22:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-indulgence, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.36,1:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,getting things,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.27,1:22:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,things that the maternal would usually supply,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.69,1:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.05,1:22:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what's lacking is the contribution
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.94,1:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the male archetype.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.34,1:23:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.00,1:23:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what's missing, the strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.38,1:23:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the kid looks inside of himself for the grit
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.19,1:23:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to carry him through, the white necklet,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.22,1:23:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.82,1:23:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So I see adequate males,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.39,1:23:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the responsibility for his children
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.85,1:23:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,as modeling and being all that you can be
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.27,1:23:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then inspiring him and giving him feedback.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.11,1:23:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I learned how to box, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.26,1:23:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the trainer, I'd give the guy a quick one and he'd say,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.38,1:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,get him, boy, get him, boy, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.96,1:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got a coach cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.76,1:23:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So these kids don't seem to have a coach cheering for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.42,1:23:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So they grab the nearest thing, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.06,1:23:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,rock stars, kick pregnant women in the belly and crap like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.14,1:23:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is pure garbage, it's garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.57,1:23:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But so I think people who are integrists should model that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.10,1:23:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and interface with the people
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.78,1:24:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and present a different alternative,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.75,1:24:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a different way to go, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.28,1:24:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.75,1:24:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.21,1:24:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.94,1:24:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.39,1:24:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.73,1:24:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.93,1:24:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be very fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.81,1:24:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Today has been magnificent. I thank both of you for devoting your life to illuminate the path just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.81,1:24:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, may I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.81,1:25:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Mary and I'm a teacher. And you had mentioned that classrooms now are about at 190 and they used to be about 400.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.39,1:25:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so my question is about how can I be a teacher and help my classes and be the best teacher that I can?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.85,1:25:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.85,1:25:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think somehow instilling pride, see? What I see lacking is pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.88,1:25:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see yourself as a victim, when anything goes, when there's no truth, when there's no integrity, when there's no answerability,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.88,1:25:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then you get a collapse of society. You get the fall of the Roman Empire. That's how it came about.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.17,1:25:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher, I think, should be, first of all, instructional, but primarily inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.17,1:25:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see my role as a teacher is to be inspirational. Convey certain data, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.31,1:25:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But then be all that you can be for them to identify with and be like that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.31,1:26:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the kind of teacher they admire. To be somebody they admire and respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.31,1:26:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And in your classroom, they somehow behave, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.31,1:26:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.03,1:26:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the kind of teacher that would make a student feel like they want to behave around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.03,1:26:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're, for example, your love is valuable.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.03,1:26:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you love that which is integrous, and you hold back from that which is not integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.32,1:26:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.35,1:26:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon they want you, they want your approval, and you become important to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.43,1:26:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, you use that relationship, the positive transference, to help train them, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.43,1:26:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The positive transference.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.48,1:26:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they must respect you as a human being, so you've got to hold yourself in high regard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.48,1:26:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And say, I'm not going to put up with that in my class.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.48,1:26:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.48,1:26:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a disciplinarian, but because of who you are, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.52,1:26:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.52,1:26:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not respecting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.52,1:26:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not going to expect me to respect you if you don't respect me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.52,1:27:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's like teaching self-esteem and self-respect, which seems to be why the classes have gone down so far.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.52,1:27:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.52,1:27:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.76,1:27:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an intellectual thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.46,1:27:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I came excited, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.77,1:27:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My first time here, and I've been, of course, an animal student for two years, and I look at my closet, I look at my bookcase,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.80,1:27:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's too many books.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.80,1:27:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like, I don't want to dump it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.80,1:27:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one book that I hold on to.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.80,1:27:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.80,1:27:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides yours, what's the calibration level of A Course in Miracles?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.80,1:27:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles, I advise people to do the workbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.80,1:27:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One sentence a day is all you can handle to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.80,1:27:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People think they can read an old chapter and get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.80,1:27:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.80,1:27:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky if you got half the first sentence, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.80,1:27:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on lesson 35.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.80,1:27:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.53,1:27:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.67,1:27:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.67,1:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do one lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.67,1:27:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do one lesson a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.98,1:27:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.98,1:27:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.98,1:27:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.98,1:27:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.98,1:27:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.98,1:27:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.98,1:27:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.98,1:27:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.98,1:27:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.98,1:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.98,1:27:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.98,1:27:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.98,1:27:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.98,1:27:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.98,1:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.10,1:28:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.39,1:28:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do one lesson a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.39,1:28:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You read the 30-35 lessons the first day.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.39,1:28:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.39,1:28:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.47,1:28:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.47,1:28:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just do one lesson a day for a year, and I would leave the textbook aside, because
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.63,1:28:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that's going to be an intellectual elaboration.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.09,1:28:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to set up a dual- set up the ego as sort of an enemy or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.28,1:28:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A Course in Miracles in and of itself, you know, calibrates the 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.31,1:28:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.47,1:28:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it says to be faithful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.31,1:28:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.27,1:28:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,means to like reflect on that sentence that day see yeah like you play with it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.26,1:28:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in your head like you hold it in your mind you know let's say it says all
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.88,1:28:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,birds are wonderful hmm you never thought of birds being wonderful then
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.56,1:28:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you start noticing you know what all birds are really wonderful so then I
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.92,1:29:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,think that's if you want one book that certainly is a great book when you get
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.56,1:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,further along you can just take the bug of a gear with you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.00,1:29:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my name is John and I was really glad to hear about Chicago
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.50,1:29:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.19,1:29:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a child in Chicago and he mentioned to me that a while back that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.52,1:29:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he had been tested for some reason he had an extremely high use of his right
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.97,1:30:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,brain it's mostly all about all he had and pretty much and he's got to like
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.51,1:30:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that but I was wondering if this is my child it's so different the way is that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.48,1:30:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,does this imply
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.28,1:30:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,some vulnerability when you're talking about different paradigm isn't going
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.35,1:30:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,between them I just wonder about
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.67,1:30:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what I'm trying to say but sometimes it seems it is very
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.14,1:30:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,vulnerable because of his way of looking at the world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.23,1:30:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how old is he he's 19's an artist 19 year old artists
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.72,1:30:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah very problem yeah I know that i really fought I'm going to move the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.81,1:30:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,paradigm
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.93,1:30:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.06,1:30:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to watch him put down the tubes, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.11,1:30:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to go to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.11,1:30:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to go to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.11,1:31:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.11,1:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.22,1:31:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He should live on the left bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.22,1:31:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In an attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.22,1:31:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With practically no money.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.05,1:31:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he could do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.05,1:31:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And around Christmas, you have to burn the furniture to stay warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.05,1:31:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.05,1:31:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in love with that paradigm, you know, La Boheme.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.07,1:31:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.07,1:31:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know La Boheme.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.07,1:31:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.07,1:31:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.07,1:31:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that, he's caught up in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.07,1:31:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a beautiful experience, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.14,1:31:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you get tired of being hungry, you get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.03,1:31:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to him a few days ago, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.03,1:31:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, if you're really unemployed, it's hard to get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.03,1:31:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.03,1:31:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, because what carries you through that, the revelation of that, is inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.03,1:31:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The dedication to one's art, the dedication to one's pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.40,1:31:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on the student, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.40,1:32:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's part of youth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.40,1:32:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he should take advantage of that inspiration while he's got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.07,1:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.18,1:32:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.18,1:32:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.00,1:32:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were going to be an artist, I'd say, God bless it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.00,1:32:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Start painting, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.22,1:32:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.22,1:32:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit driving a cab.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.39,1:32:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some paint in the canvas.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.39,1:32:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.39,1:32:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to the left bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.31,1:32:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, move to the left bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.31,1:32:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to find a girlfriend named Mimi.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.44,1:32:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to get a chest x-ray, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.52,1:32:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I basically just want to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.52,1:32:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.52,1:33:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as humans, we're on the earth school, and we continue to learn and evolve, and become more conscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.96,1:33:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering, I don't know if you can tell me,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.96,1:33:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you can answer this question or not, because you're not there yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.96,1:33:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but when you die, will you be evolving and continuing to gain more consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.96,1:33:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will your calibration go up?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.96,1:33:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I die, will my calibration go up?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.96,1:33:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would imagine it would disappear altogether.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.96,1:33:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there the possibility to become an archangel?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.96,1:33:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what the ultimate destiny is.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.96,1:33:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.68,1:33:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everything of oneness does not have gradations.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.14,1:33:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The quality of oneness does not have gradations.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.40,1:34:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from outside the reality that it seems to.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.47,1:34:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,From within the reality, each thing is complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.31,1:34:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.31,1:34:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to be gained.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.50,1:34:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, there isn't the fantasy of being promoted to archangel.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.00,1:34:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hell of a job, to tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.00,1:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned it down, and I said no.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.00,1:34:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wanted it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.00,1:34:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the waiting list, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.39,1:34:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you're done, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.85,1:34:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the completeness of the totality is complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.85,1:35:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then whatever the reality is to the evolution of consciousness, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.88,1:35:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.88,1:35:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is that which helps support the advancement of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.88,1:35:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then it serves by virtue of what it is, not by virtue of what it does, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.88,1:35:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the completion is already complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.56,1:35:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we made it by five.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.56,1:35:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At five, they're sending in the cops.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.69,1:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It said to be done by five.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.69,1:35:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're all supposed to be good little scouts and pick up our good campers
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.69,1:35:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring our stuff with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.69,1:35:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been exquisite.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.02,1:35:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.19,1:35:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more I could desire or wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.35,1:36:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is completely 100% complete at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.35,1:36:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They would like you to do a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.35,1:36:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.35,1:36:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.35,1:36:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.35,1:36:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to pray on top of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.35,1:36:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we thank thee for the blessing of our existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.27,1:36:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For the blessing of our existence, which is already the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.27,1:36:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencing of our own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.27,1:36:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for the awareness of the reality and the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.50,1:36:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the source of our existence for its own sake,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.56,1:36:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to reflect back that reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.97,1:36:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are thankful to be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.21,1:36:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think thankful together to be again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.39,1:36:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.68,1:37:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have been here together like a flock of birds many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.68,1:37:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we've swooped into this little place now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.68,1:37:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll all be swooping out.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.68,1:37:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God knows, where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.68,1:37:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to go ahead and signal back to you where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.68,1:37:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.68,1:37:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for your presence, Jeff.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.68,1:37:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going as a flock?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.56,1:37:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.56,1:37:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the same place in the celestial realm, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.56,1:37:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we come and return to the same place in the celestial realm.
